    <item>
      <title>维旺迪弃权 意大利电信老板有望连任</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/vivendi-abstain-telecom-italia-board-renewal-vote-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利电信 (TIM) 老板彼得罗·拉布里奥拉 (Pietro Labriola) 似乎有望获得连任，此前主要投资者维旺迪 (Vivendi) 决定在股东投票中就前电话垄断巨头董事会的更新问题投弃权票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/media-telecom/vivendi-abstain-telecom-italia-board-renewal-vote-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 16:41:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
